vtm: vtm (a text-based user interface)
vtm:
vtm: It is a text-based application where the entire user interface is 
vtm: represented by a mosaic of text cells forming a TUI matrix. The 
vtm: resulting TUI matrix is just rendered either into its own GUI window
vtm: or into a compatible text console.
vtm:
vtm: It can wrap any console application and be nested indefinitely, 
vtm: forming a text-based desktop environment.
vtm:
vtm:
